weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute

Class TweetCentroid

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.filters.Filter
      • weka.filters.SimpleFilter
        • weka.filters.SimpleBatchFilter
          • weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute.TweetCentroid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, CapabilitiesHandler, CapabilitiesIgnorer, CommandlineRunnable, OptionHandler, RevisionHandler

    public class TweetCentroid
extends SimpleBatchFilter
    Given a corpus of documents creates Vector Space model for each word using bag-of-words and cluster-based attributes.

    $Revision: 1 $
    Author:
    Felipe Bravo-Marquez (fbravoma@waikato.ac.nz)
